description.en: Pomskey is a token on the Binance Smart Chain boasting a number of impressive features. Pomskey is programmed to reward holders and is built on transparency and trust. We are set out to continue to build upon the work of previous projects and go to new heights. By combining an innovative Auto-liquidity feature that increases liquidity of the token rapidly, have a large burn rate in place, and most importantly a reward system for all holders. With all of these features together we can have a power house token that is ready to give back to the community.
